,"e":"you see","i":"تُبۡصِرُوۡنَۙ"}],"a":{"g":"So I swear by what you see"}},"39":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.55","c":"وَمَا","d":"wamā","e":"And what","i":"وَمَا"},{"b":"0.66","h":"1.34","c":"لَا","d":"lā","e":"not","i":"لَا"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.89","c":"تُبۡصِرُونَ","d":"tub'ṣirūna","e":"you see","i":"تُبۡصِرُوۡنَۙ"}],"a":{"g":"And what you do not see"}},"40":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.25","c":"إِنَّهُۥ","d":"innahu","e":"Indeed it (is)","i":"اِنَّهٗ"},{"b":"1.8","h":"1.99","c":"لَقَوۡلُ","d":"laqawlu","e":"surely (the) Word","i":"لَقَوۡلُ"},{"b":"2.5","h":"3.1","c":"رَسُولٖ","d":"rasūlin","e":"(of) a Messenger","i":"رَسُوۡلٍ"},{"b":"4.6","h":"4.95","c":"كَرِيمٖ","d":"karīmin","e":"noble","i":"كَرِيۡمٍۚۙ"}],"a":{"g":"[That] indeed, the Qur'an is the word of a noble Messenger."}},"41":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.2","c":"وَمَا","d":"wamā","e":"And not","i":"وَّمَا"},{"b":"0.64","h":"0.97","c":"هُوَ","d":"huwa","e":"it","i":"هُوَ"},{"b":"1.1","h":"1.64","c":"بِقَوۡلِ","d":"biqawli","e":"(is the) word","i":"بِقَوۡلِ"},{"b":"1.9","h":"2.72","c":"شَاعِرٖۚ","d":"shāʿirin","e":"(of) a poet;","i":"شَاعِرٍؕ"},{"b":"2.8","h":"5.35","c":"قَلِيلٗا","d":"qalīlan","e":"little","i":"قَلِيۡلًا"},{"b":"4.0","h":"7.07","c":"مَّا","d":"mā","e":"(is) what","i":"مَّا"},{"b":"5.3","h":"7.58","c":"تُؤۡمِنُونَ","d":"tu'minūna","e":"you believe!","i":"تُؤۡمِنُوۡنَۙ"}],"a":{"g":"And it is not the word of a poet; little do you believe."}},"42":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.15","c":"وَلَا","d":"walā","e":"And not","i":"وَلَا"},{"b":"0.6","h":"1.01","c":"بِقَوۡلِ","d":"biqawli","e":"(it is the) word","i":"بِقَوۡلِ"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.22","c":"كَاهِنٖۚ","d":"kāhinin","e":"(of) a soothsayer;","i":"كَاهِنٍؕ"},{"b":"2.7","h":"5.85","c":"قَلِيلٗا","d":"qalīlan","e":"little","i":"قَلِيۡلًا"},{"b":"3.5","h":"7.65","c":"مَّا","d":"mā","e":"(is) what","i":"مَّا"},{"b":"4.7","h":"8.18","c":"تَذَكَّرُونَ","d":"tadhakkarūna","e":"you remember","i":"تَذَكَّرُوۡنَؕ"}],"a":{"g":"Nor the word of a soothsayer; little do you