","e":"one","i":"اَحَدٍ"},{"b":"3.9","h":"5.34","c":"عَنۡهُ","d":"ʿanhu","e":"[from him]","i":"عَنۡهُ"},{"b":"4.6","h":"6.23","c":"حَٰجِزِينَ","d":"ḥājizīna","e":"(could) prevent","i":"حَاجِزِيۡنَ"}],"a":{"g":"And there is no one of you who could prevent [Us] from him."}},"48":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.3","c":"وَإِنَّهُۥ","d":"wa-innahu","e":"And indeed it","i":"وَاِنَّهٗ"},{"b":"1.9","h":"2.3","c":"لَتَذۡكِرَةٞ","d":"latadhkiratun","e":"(is) surely a reminder","i":"لَتَذۡكِرَةٌ"},{"b":"3.2","h":"4.41","c":"لِّلۡمُتَّقِينَ","d":"lil'muttaqīna","e":"for the Allah-fearing","i":"لِّلۡمُتَّقِيۡنَ"}],"a":{"g":"And indeed, the Qur'an is a reminder for the righteous."}},"49":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.36","c":"وَإِنَّا","d":"wa-innā","e":"And indeed We","i":"وَاِنَّا"},{"b":"1.6","h":"2.1","c":"لَنَعۡلَمُ","d":"lanaʿlamu","e":"surely know","i":"لَنَعۡلَمُ"},{"b":"2.6","h":"3.46","c":"أَنَّ","d":"anna","e":"that","i":"اَنَّ"},{"b":"3.7","h":"4.8","c":"مِنكُم","d":"minkum","e":"among you","i":"مِنۡكُمۡ"},{"b":"5.6","h":"6.99","c":"مُّكَذِّبِينَ","d":"mukadhibīna","e":"(are) deniers","i":"مُّكَذِّبِيۡنَ"}],"a":{"g":"And indeed, We know that among you are deniers."}},"50":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.35","c":"وَإِنَّهُۥ","d":"wa-innahu","e":"And indeed it","i":"وَاِنَّهٗ"},{"b":"1.7","h":"2.37","c":"لَحَسۡرَةٌ","d":"laḥasratun","e":"(is) surely a regret","i":"لَحَسۡرَةٌ"},{"b":"2.9","h":"3.99","c":"عَلَى","d":"ʿalā","e":"upon","i":"عَلَى"},{"b":"3.4","h":"4.63","c":"ٱلۡكَٰفِرِينَ","d":"l-kāfirīna","e":"the disbelievers","i":"الۡكٰفِرِيۡنَ"}],"a":{"g":"And indeed, it will be [a cause of] regret upon the disbelievers."}},"51":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"وَإِنَّهُۥ","d":"wa-innahu","e":"And indeed it (is)","i":"وَاِنَّهٗ"},{"b":"1.9","h":"2.11","c":"لَحَقُّ","d":"laḥaqqu","e":"surely (the) truth","i":"لَحَـقُّ"},{"b":"2.7","h":"3.28","c":"ٱلۡيَقِينِ","d":"l-yaqīni","e":"(of) certainty","i":"الۡيَقِيۡنِ"}],"a":{"g":"And indeed, it is the truth of certainty."}},"52":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.35","c":"فَسَبِّحۡ","d":"fasabbiḥ","e":"So glorify","i":"فَسَبِّحۡ"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.6","c":"بِٱسۡمِ","d":"bi-is'mi","e":"(the) name","i":"بِاسۡمِ"},{"b":"1.5","h":"2.31","c":"رَبِّكَ","d":"rabbika","e":"(of) your Lord","i":"رَبِّكَ"},{"b":"2.4","h":"3.55","c":"ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","d":"l-ʿaẓīmi","e":"the Most Great","i":"الۡعَظِيۡمِ"}],"a":{"g":"So exalt the name of your Lord, the Most Great."}}}